OL,3,CThe 'crucial' exercise involving boats
OL,4,Cand aircraft happening off Cornish
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FThe Maritime and Coastguard Agency has
OL,8,Fcarried out a 'crucial' counter-
OL,9,Fpollution exercise in Cornwall aimed
OL,10,Fat tackling pollution.
OL,12,FCrews off the coast of Falmouth are
OL,13,Flearning how to deal with oil spills
OL,14,Fusing a new piece of a equipment.
OL,16,FStan Woznicki, MCA Head of Counter
OL,17,FPollution and Salvage, said: "We are
OL,18,Flaunching a one stop oil recovery and
OL,19,Fcontainment system, which we use to
OL,20,Fconfine oil then collect it and move
OL,21,Fit into a storage facility.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
