OL,3,CThe 'crucial' exercise involving boats
OL,4,Cand aircraft happening off Cornish
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,F"This is a very relatively new
OL,8,Fcapability but it's a one stop shop."
OL,10,FStan said there is a variety of other
OL,11,Ftools available for tackling oil
OL,12,Fspills depending on their size and
OL,13,Flocation.
OL,15,F"We have to be prepared for a whole
OL,16,Fpile of different options".
OL,18,F"We use a lot of capability to meet
OL,19,Fthe oil product and the environmental
OL,20,Fconditions".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
