OL,4,Cand aircraft happening off Cornish
OL,5,Ccoast
OL,7,FHe added the drill is crucial to
OL,8,Ftackling oil spills.
OL,10,F"Oil is dreadful for the environment,
OL,11,Fyou've got to get to it quickly, if
OL,12,Fyou leave it, it spreads - therefore
OL,13,Fyour problem gets bigger.
OL,15,F"The aim is to get to the scene as
OL,16,Fquickly as you can, collect it before
OL,17,Fthe oil has a chance to spread.
