OL,7,F"Various oils spread at different
OL,8,Frates, some of them are easier, some
OL,9,Fof them are harder to collect, so we
OL,10,Fhave a range of options we can use,
OL,11,Fbut it has to be removed from the
OL,12,Fenvironment because it can have a long
OL,13,Fterm effect."
